        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Don't Wait for August 2025 Enforcement
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8">
          Start your EU AI Act compliance journey today. Expert assessment and implementation guidance 
          available for immediate deployment.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-lg text-european-blue bg-white hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colours shadow-lg">
            Book Assessment Now
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border-2 border-white text-base font-medium rounded-lg text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-european-blue transition-colours">
            View Services
